        h2 Who is this course for?
        | Do you want to join the new economy but can't just quit your current job? Then this is the course for you! I will teach you how to master HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and more. So you can do what I did and create a thriving career for yourself in the growing tech sector!
        br
        br
        | This will be the 
